te.
Jakulo tzʼok jun ninqʼij te tzalajbʼil ex te mujbʼabʼil noqwit mintiʼ
aye tx´olb´ab´il kyi´j xjal n-el kyi´n, kyi´j nya b´a´n nya b´a´n, axpe ikx kyi´j kyimni jalin
n-chi yek´un ch´ixmi tkyaqil q´ij toj Profeta. At maj a Bill extzen a Mr.
