OWLs moqa NEWTs at jun xjal at? Ax tok mya ikyjo. . . . Tkyaqil k-xel b´inchen
ti´j t-xilen aq´untl tzaj tk´amo´n, ti´j t-xilen t-xnaq´tzb´il
yek´unte.
