kye. A seguridad o tz´ok t-ximan jun syent maj toj amb´il te q´ijel.
“B´a´n ikyjo,” chi Harry, n-chi tzyet tu´n t-xi tna´n t-xob´il tu´n tpaj mya b´a´n
onb´il, “n-ximane qa noq o´kx k-xel n-watl tzalu exttzen n-chi ayon ti´j
nchi´j."
