mya tzmaxi aj t-xi´ t-spik´umal q´an t-spik´umal lajaj tqan t-xilen kyi´j,
extzen a Harry otaq tz´el t-xo´n t-xb´alun te Invisibilidad tun t-xi´
tzaj tka´yin, qa el tniky´ ti´j, tuk´e jun t-xilen t-xob´il, aju uplit
t-xu´k t-xu´k extzen t-xmakal Severus Snape nim, q´eq, extzen t-xmakal.
“b´a´n, b´a´n, b´a´n,” chi Snape, tzaj t-xo´n t-xob´il extzen tzaj t-xo´n jun maj aju´ candado, tun t-xi´ ky-b´et aye cadenas t-xe´ extzen aye
aye ttzi ja n-chi jaqet. “B´a´n t-ximana tu´n t-xi´ya, Potter, maske teya
qʼanchaʼlxix qa o kubʼ kyximen qa aju tuʼn tok kyqʼoʼn kyxbʼalun xjal toj tja xnaqʼtzbʼil, kbʼel tnajsaʼn kywitze».
“Mya b´a´n tu´n n-ch´expu´ne, mya b´a´n wune —” tzaj tzyet tu´n Harry, extzun Snape
t-xaq twitz.
“Mya il ti´j tu´n t-ximana, Nymphadora, a Potter b´a´n t-xilen —
